Mockup Description for Geographic Intelligence (Version 2 - Improved Layout)

Improved layout for Geographic Intelligence.

Changes:
- Interactive Mapbox integration with better controls
- Added overlay options for different data layers
- Improved filter panel

Layout:
- Top: Comprehensive filter bar
- Center: Interactive map with multiple overlays
- Bottom: Data insights and export options

Hierarchy:
- Primary: Map with overlays
- Secondary: Filters and insights

Usability:
- Better zoom, layer toggles, data export